    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this stunning vehicle that is in absolute mint condition! It looks and drives exactly like it just rolled off the showroom floor, with a flawless exterior and an interior that still feels brand new. This is a rare find for anyone seeking a car in perfect, pristine shape\u2014truly the gold standard for its model!",
      "price": 49500.0,
